# Trump Tweet Visualize - Layer 1

Weekly mention-network pipeline and web app for `tweets_01-08-2021.csv`.

## Setup

```bash
pip install -e .
```

## Build Artifacts

```bash
python -m trump_graph build --input tweets_01-08-2021.csv --out data/processed --min-mention-count 1 --include-retweets
```

## Run App

```bash
streamlit run app/main.py
```

## Run Tests

```bash
pytest -q
```
